Download the latest build from http://wbemservices.sourceforge.net/ 
and copy here the following jars from the lib directory -

wbem.jar

and the following jars from the cimom/lib directory -

cimom.jar  
cimrepository.jar  

and the following jars from the bin directory -

mofcomp.jar

